    "id": "11",
    "title": "Carbonara (real)",
    "description": "These days, so many carbonara recipes cheat with cream which is a shame. The traditional method uses raw egg which is mixed vigorously with hot pasta and parmigiana reggiano cheese which transforms into a silky, creamy, luxurious sauce…",
    "image": "/recipe-images/recipe-11.jpg",
    "difficulty": "Advanced",
